es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.generation

Interface NormGenerationMachine

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CBRNormGenerationMachine

    public interface NormGenerationMachine
    A norm generation machine generates norms from conflicts. Each generated norm is aimed to regulate the given conflict, trying to prevent it from happening again in the future
    Author:
    "Javier Morales (jmorales@iiia.csic.es)"
    See Also:
    Goal, Conflict

                                   DomainFunctions dmInputs,
